description: Essity AB engages in the development, production, and marketing of personal care products. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm and currently employs 46,084 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2017-06-15. The firm conducts sales in about 150 countries under such brands, as TENA for incontinence products and Tork for Away-from-Home tissue, as well as under other brands, such as Bodyform, Velvet, Cushelle and Plenty. The Company’s medical brands comprise Leukoplast, Cutimed, JOBST, Delta Cast, Delta Lite and Actimove.
